OL,3,CGisele Pelicot's ex-husband praises
OL,4,Cher courage in coming forward
OL,6,FFor the last time, Dominique Pelicot,
OL,7,Fwho allegedly drugged his wife so he
OL,8,Fcould film strangers having sex with
OL,9,Fher, has appealed to the court - and
OL,10,Fhis family. Chloe Keedy was in Avignon
OL,12,FGisele Pelicot arrived at court this
OL,13,Fmorning knowing that at least one part
OL,14,Fof her ordeal was almost over.
OL,16,FBut in France, it's the accused that
OL,17,Fget the final word, so she listened as
OL,18,Fdozens of men charged with her rape
OL,19,Fwere given their chance to address the
OL,20,Fcourt.
