OL,6,FThey are men of all ages, from all
OL,7,Fwalks of life. There is a nurse, a
OL,8,Fjournalist, a soldier, a prison guard
OL,9,F- almost all with one thing in common.
OL,10,FThey are accused of travelling at
OL,11,Fnight to the Pelicot's home in the
OL,12,FProvencal village of Mazan, and raping
OL,13,Fher while she lay in a drug-induced
OL,14,Fcoma.
