OL,3,CGisele Pelicot's ex-husband praises
OL,4,Cher courage in coming forward
OL,6,FThe first to speak was Gisele
OL,7,FPelicot's former husband, Dominique.
OL,8,FHe has admitted repeatedly drugging
OL,9,Fand raping his wife over the course of
OL,10,Falmost a decade, and inviting dozens
OL,11,Fof strangers into their bedroom to
OL,12,Fjoin in.
OL,14,FHe used his moment to ask for his
OL,15,Ffamily's forgiveness. He began by
OL,16,Ftelling the court that he wanted to
OL,17,Fpraise his wife's courage during the
OL,18,Ftrial. He said he regretted what he
OL,19,Fhad done, adding, "I have been called
OL,20,Fmany names, but I rather intend to be
OL,21,Fforgotten".
