OL,6,F"It's been harder than anything she
OL,7,Fcould have expected or could have
OL,8,Fimagined," Stephane Babonneau said.
OL,9,F"But she never regretted it, because
OL,10,Fit's been important for everyone. For
OL,11,Fother victims, for women in general."
OL,13,FHe said the support she has received
OL,14,Ffrom all over the world has given her
OL,15,Fthe strength to go on.
